 Segun  A contemporary music worshipper, Segun is a Lagos-based phenomenal songwriter and a games/animation concept artiste. From interesting production to well-crafted lyrics, the song came handy. Since the release of Said And Done, music lovers and fans have shown excitement and have lauded the singer for its message at a time the world is on standstill. “It’s so peaceful and fun to do this song,” he said. Said and Done is the artiste’s first single in 2020, as he’s currently working on his EP, GIFT- God Is Forever Tangible. 